Package commands

package commands
  • Class
    Description
    Add
    Command for adding study groups to the collection from console.
    AddFromFile
    Command for adding study groups to the collection from file.
    AddIfMax
    Command that adds a study group to the collection only if it is the largest from console.
    AddIfMaxFromFile
    Command that adds a study group to the collection only if it is the largest from file.
    Clear
    Command that clears the entire collection.
    Command
     
    Commands
    Enum representing available commands in the system.
    CountByGroupAdmin
    Command that counts the number of study groups where a specified person is the admin from console.
    CountByGroupAdminFromFile
    Command that counts the number of study groups where a specified person is the admin from file.
    ExecuteScript
    Command that executes a script from a specified file.
    Exit
    Command that exits the program.
    GroupCountingById
    Command that groups study groups by ID and counts the number of elements in each group.
    Help
    Command that provides information about available commands.
    Helpable
    Interface for commands that provide help information.
    Info
    Command that provides information about the collection.
    RemoveAnyByGroupAdmin
    Command that removes a study group by its group admin from console.
    RemoveAnyByGroupAdminFromFile
    Command that removes a study group by its group admin from file.
    RemoveById
    Command that removes a study group by its ID.
    RemoveGreater
    Command that removes study groups greater than a given one from the collection from console.
    RemoveGreaterFromFile
    Command that removes study groups greater than a given one from the collection from file.
    RemoveLower
    Command that removes study groups lower than a given one from the collection from console.
    RemoveLowerFromFile
    Command that removes study groups lower than a given one from the collection from file.
    Save
    Command that saves the collection data to a file.
    Show
    Command that shows all study groups in the collection.
    Update
    Command that updates a study group in the collection by its ID from console.
    UpdateFromFile
    Command that updates a study group in the collection by its ID from file.
